media.altText:
A six panel comic of Ky trying to help Honeydew out of depression. The comic is titled "Supportive Patience" and is made by Theresa Scovil.

Panel 1:
Honeydew is incredibly sad as a they're covered in darkness.
Ky comes up and happily says "I love you."
Panel 2:
Honeydew doesn't react in any way. This surprises Ky.
Panel 3:
Ky gives a sympathetic smile and says "You're amazing."
Panel 4:
Again, Honeydew doesn't react. Ky becomes sad.
Panel 5:
Ky sighs.
Panel 6:
Ky gives a sad smile and tells Honeydew "I'll just wait for you here."
